---
title: Smart Plant-Based Ground Protein and Cheddar Patties with Maple-BBQ Sauce and Fresh Salad
description: These flavours will leave your tastebuds begging for more! Savoury plant-based ground protein patties are basted in maple-BBQ sauce and topped with sharp cheddar. A fresh apple-and-cranberry-topped salad makes this meal both delicious and nutritious!
